<header class="header">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    This policy explains what information GrowByDate.com collects, how it is used, and how third-party services such as analytics providers and affiliate programs may process information.
  </p>
</header>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com does not require user accounts and does not collect personal information directly from visitors through account registration, checkout forms, or user profiles.
  </p>

  <p>
    Like most websites, GrowByDate.com may collect basic non-identifying information automatically through analytics tools, hosting services, browser logs, or similar technologies, such as:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Browser type</li>
    <li>Device type</li>
    <li>Operating system</li>
    <li>General geographic region</li>
    <li>Pages visited</li>
    <li>Referring pages</li>
    <li>Approximate time spent on the site</li>
    <li>Date and time of visits</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    This information is used to understand how visitors use the site, improve content, monitor performance, and maintain the security and reliability of the website.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com may use cookies or similar technologies to improve site performance, analyze traffic, remember basic preferences, and support affiliate-link functionality.
  </p>

  <p>
    Cookies are small text files stored on your device. Some cookies may be set by GrowByDate.com, while others may be set by third-party services used on the site, such as analytics providers or affiliate networks.
  </p>

  <p>
    You can disable or delete cookies through your browser settings. Some parts of the site may not function as intended if cookies are disabled.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Analytics</h2>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com may use analytics tools to understand how visitors interact with the site. These tools may collect information such as pages visited, device type, browser type, general location, referring pages, and interactions with the website.
  </p>

  <p>
    Analytics information is used in aggregate to improve articles, site navigation, performance, and user experience.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com participates in affiliate advertising programs, including the Amazon Associates Program.
  </p>

  <p>
    As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases.
  </p>

  <p>
    Some pages may contain affiliate links. If you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, GrowByDate.com may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you.
  </p>

  <p>
    Affiliate links may include tracking identifiers or use cookies and similar technologies that allow affiliate partners, including Amazon, to determine that you clicked a link from GrowByDate.com.
  </p>

  <p>
    Once you click an affiliate link, you will be directed to a third-party website. Your activity on that third-party website is governed by that website’s own privacy policy, terms, and cookie practices.
  </p>

  <p>
    Affiliate partnerships do not influence recommendations. Products are mentioned only when relevant to the topic.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com may use third-party services such as hosting providers, analytics providers, affiliate networks, advertising partners, or embedded content providers.
  </p>

  <p>
    These third-party services may collect, process, or store information according to their own privacy policies. GrowByDate.com does not control how third-party services collect or use information once you interact with them.
  </p>

  <p>
    Third-party services used by the site may include, but are not limited to:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Cloudflare Pages for website hosting and performance</li>
    <li>Analytics tools for traffic measurement and site improvement</li>
    <li>Amazon Associates and other affiliate programs for referral tracking</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>External Links</h2>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com may link to external websites, including retailers, product pages, reference sources, and other third-party resources.
  </p>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com is not responsible for the privacy practices, content, or policies of external websites. You should review the privacy policy of any third-party website you visit.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Data Security</h2>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com is a static website hosted on Cloudflare Pages. The site does not maintain user accounts, process payments, or intentionally store sensitive personal information.
  </p>

  <p>
    Reasonable steps are taken to maintain the security and reliability of the website. However, no website or internet transmission can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com is intended for a general audience and is not directed at children under the age of 13.
  </p>

  <p>
    GrowByDate.com does not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided personal information to the site, please contact us so the information can be reviewed and removed if necessary.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Your Choices</h2>

  <p>
    You can control cookies through your browser settings. You can also use browser privacy features, ad-blocking tools, or tracking-prevention settings to limit certain types of tracking.
  </p>

  <p>
    If you do not want affiliate partners to receive referral information, you should avoid clicking affiliate links or adjust your browser privacy settings accordingly.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="card">
  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>

  <p>
    This privacy policy may be updated as GrowByDate.com evolves, including when new services, analytics tools, affiliate programs, or site features are added.
  </p>

  <p>
    Updates will be reflected on this page. The most recent version of the policy will always be available at this URL.
  </p>
</section>

